# CateringPromoCopy Component Rules

## Overview

Rules for `src/components/molecules/CateringPromoCopy.tsx`

## Purpose

Molecule that renders the promo heading, paragraphs, and CTA using constants and atoms.

## Rules

- ✅ Data Source: Read from `CATERING_PROMO` in `@/constants/catering`.
- ✅ Composition: Use `ButtonLink` atom for CTA.
- ✅ Typography: `h2` uses `text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold`, paragraphs `text-gray-700` with spacing `mb-4` / `mb-6`.
- ✅ No props (content centralized in constants).
- ✅ Export both named and default.

## Template

```tsx
<h2>{CATERING_PROMO.heading}</h2>
<p>{CATERING_PROMO.lead}</p>
<p>{CATERING_PROMO.body}</p>
<ButtonLink href={CATERING_PROMO.cta.href}>{CATERING_PROMO.cta.label}</ButtonLink>
```

## QA Checklist

- Text matches constants exactly.
- CTA href/label matches constants.
- Heading has role heading level 2.
